<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2065062" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">（多图）<br><br>当然啊。<br><br>外表不仅仅是五官气质，更是窥探内心的终端。<br>牛逼的人都是善于通过各种手段伪装和掩饰自己真实想法的人。<br><br>俗话说，眼睛是心灵的窗户。<br>所以一般眼镜片能反光的都是高手。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/0623e474f27a62e981760b165fad5f89_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image" width="259"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image lazy" width="259" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/0623e474f27a62e981760b165fad5f89_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/a95cd4fa63a67d25b384b9d264da4e28_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image" width="259"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="259" data-rawheight="194" class="content_image lazy" width="259" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/a95cd4fa63a67d25b384b9d264da4e28_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/27d58e8d40f2cc00f94499245b93b93c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="549" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="550" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/27d58e8d40f2cc00f94499245b93b93c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="550" data-rawheight="549" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="550" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/27d58e8d40f2cc00f94499245b93b93c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/27d58e8d40f2cc00f94499245b93b93c_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/646dacc09765d8d584fb18154e1e8983_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="338" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/646dacc09765d8d584fb18154e1e8983_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="338" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/646dacc09765d8d584fb18154e1e8983_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/646dacc09765d8d584f